Wal-Mart Encouraged by S. Africa Consumer Market, McMillon Says

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-06-29T16:21:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-29/wal-mart-encouraged-by-south-african-consumer-market-ceo-mcmillon-says.html
Wal-Mart Stores Inc. (WMT) ’s Chief
Executive Officer Doug McMillon said he is “very encouraged”
about consumer demand in South Africa and sub-Saharan Africa has
become “more attractive.”  Massmart Holdings Ltd. (MSM) , the South African retailer that is
51 percent owned by Wal-Mart, has an organizational culture
that’s a “good fit” with the world’s largest retailer,
McMillon said in an interview on Johannesburg-based 702 Talk
Radio today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  